  "prompt": "Which is the best plan for international calling in India for people in UAE?",
  "response": "When looking for the best international calling plan from India for people in the UAE, you should consider several factors, including call rates, available packages, network coverage, and customer service. Here are some popular options to consider:\n\n1. **Local Indian Telecom Operators**:\n   - **Airtel**: Offers international calling packs that can be added to prepaid and postpaid plans. They often provide good rates for calling the UAE specifically.\n   - **Vodafone Idea (Vi)**: Provides international calling packs that include rates for calling various countries, including the UAE.\n   - **Jio**: Also has international calling packs with competitive rates. Jio's app can be handy for managing international calls.\n\n2. **Calling Apps**:\n   - **WhatsApp, Skype, or Google Duo**: Utilizing internet-based calling apps can significantly reduce costs. These apps allow free calls if both parties have the app installed and are connected to the internet.\n   - **Rebtel**: This service allows calling without internet access and often has competitive rates for international calls.\n\n3. **Virtual Calling Services**:\n   - Services like **Localphone** or **Viber Out** can offer inexpensive rates and are especially useful for making calls when you are on the move.\n\n4. **International Calling Cards**:\n   - Prepaid international calling cards can also be a good option. They often provide specific rates for calling particular countries, including the UAE.\n\n5. **Check Promotions and Offers**: Operators frequently have promotional offers or discounts for international calling. It's advisable to check their websites or contact customer support for the latest deals.\n\nBefore choosing a plan, compare the rates, features, and reviews of each option based on your calling needs. Consider the frequency and duration of your calls to ensure the selected plan suits your lifestyle.",
